snippet.title: VETITUM_VRC LAUNCH TRAILER | OCTOBER 31
snippet.description:
You have been called for the investigation of what happened in the Flemmywoods forest, you must analyze all the tape of the video game to each existing area, every detail and find out who is behind this.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3182200/VETITUM_VRC/
